{"tid":1553740,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【激烈召集】聚集「光復香港」，留低「時代革命」！","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T07:47:07.000Z","uid":280978,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"730400b813b6f83a0d702368ae51e5dcbe4c9a54","tid":1553740,"uid":280978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/5A34/production/_108229032_gettyimages-1159723718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F5A34%2Fproduction%2F_108229032_gettyimages-1159723718.jpg&h=2a483cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（圖片來源：BBC）</span><br />\n話說喺呢場運動入面，每次上街都會見到有手足用噴漆寫字畫公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且有好多都好靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image5.thenewslens.com/2019/8/ke6xk2dwikyuvfzv9usvkhy1plxa0g.jpg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage5.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F8%2Fke6xk2dwikyuvfzv9usvkhy1plxa0g.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=1fe902a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（圖片來源：關鍵評論網）</span><br />\n<br />\n但<strong>問題係</strong>呢啲塗鴉往往都<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好快就會被清理</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有件及此<br />\n<strong>我同朋友希望可以整條片／album，影低曬啲塗鴉</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>作爲對呢場運動一個特別嘅記錄</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以</span></strong><br />\n希望各位巴絲手足可以幫幫手<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">分享下你哋影到嘅塗鴉！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相／片都得！<br />\n（方便嘅可以寫埋個塗鴉嘅地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cc1874fdeb52396cfebc34e22dc57c3ca9a329a2","tid":1553740,"uid":25375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"每次發夢都冇影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c459453e9b07c915f5aff3434aeaf02765ce1a25","tid":1553740,"uid":312554,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:03:09.000Z","msg":"葵涌<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CKbj5JW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCKbj5JW.jpg&h=deb54eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvRW7Xj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnvRW7Xj.jpg&h=8ba20740&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cc2adf952170837f1b8d9004da09296e8462c3a","tid":1553740,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"137ed27df491d429d8c8accdf82894f492828ddd","tid":1553740,"uid":280978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c459453e9b07c915f5aff3434aeaf02765ce1a25","tid":1553740,"uid":312554,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:03:09.000Z","msg":"葵涌<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CKbj5JW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCKbj5JW.jpg&h=deb54eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvRW7Xj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnvRW7Xj.jpg&h=8ba20740&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"好靚！！！多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138b05878451a89e4c607ff16d8ba87f3358c0ff","tid":1553740,"uid":6534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c806fb18571b291cd4ddf6ae354b1077b8cf78e0","tid":1553740,"uid":109238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:05:55.000Z"